<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 06:32:23 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>【財政預算案 2022】創新科技產業發展 5 大措施　50 億「策略性創科基金」+大學科技初創資助</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/23/budget-speech/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=budget-speech</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 06:32:23 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[城中熱話]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1087456</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>2022-23 年度財政預算案今日（23 曰）宣讀，除了投入資金於民生舒困及土地房屋等傳統項目外，今年政府亦大額支 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="p1"><span class="s1">2022-23</span><span class="s2">年度財政預算案今日（23 曰）宣讀，除了投入資金於民生舒困及土地房屋等傳統項目外，今年政府亦大額支援於</span><span class="s2">創新科技產業發展。</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s2">港府成立</span><span class="s1">50</span><span class="s2">億「策略性創科基金」，</span><span class="s2">投資對香港具戰略價值，具規模和發展潛力的本地及非本地科技企業，吸引它們在港落戶或擴充，或與本地科技企業建立合作夥伴關係。</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s2">「大學科技初創企業資助計劃」（</span><span class="s1">TSSSU ），</span><span class="s2">大學資助額由每年</span><span class="s1">800</span><span class="s2">萬倍增至</span><span class="s1">1600</span><span class="s2">萬。每間大學的新</span><span class="s2">初創團隊亦受惠於 <span class="s1">TSSSU</span>，提供額外與<span class="s1">1:1</span>私人投資</span><span class="s2">的配對資助，</span><span class="s2">每年最多獲</span><span class="s1">150</span><span class="s2">萬配對資助，資助最長</span><span class="s1">3</span><span class="s2">年。</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s2">政府將預留<span class="s1">100</span>億推動「生命健康」科研，設立「<span class="s1">InnoLife Health Tech Hub </span>生命健康科研中心」、提供</span><span class="s2">完備硬件、科研人才、臨床試驗及數據應用配套，以</span><span class="s2">提升科研容量及能力</span><span class="s2">，建立更完善的產業鏈</span><span class="s3">。</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">政府計劃在本港<span class="s2">倍增國家重點實驗室</span><span class="s2">及對國家工程技術研究中心香港分中心的資助，每年總資助額增至 4.4 億，以</span></span><span class="s2">推動科技應用及</span><span class="s2">研發。</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s2">另外將預留</span><span class="s1">6</span><span class="s2">億進行全面的電子政府審計，更好</span><span class="s2">利用資訊科技工具，</span><span class="s2">如雲計算、大數據、</span><span class="s1">AI</span><span class="s2">、區塊鏈等</span><span class="s2">推行和優化數碼政府服務。</span></p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料來源</span><span class="s2">：<a href="https://www.budget.gov.hk/2022/chi/re.html">2022-2023 年度政府財政預算案</a></span></p><p class="p2">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
